headline: Marjorie Taylor Greene Is Buying These 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks. Should You?
summary: It's not always easy for a member of the U.S. House of Representatives to secure a spot in the limelight.  Rep. Marjorie Taylor Greene (R-Ga.) is one of them.  Greene's political moves often make the news.
